as a reference.

Or you can simply meditate with a simple mantra such as "om namashshivaayai" 
or "om shivaayai namaH" or "om namashshivaayai cha namashshivaaya" or a 
shloka.

It is possible to do a homam to Parvati also. Mahalakshmi homam can be used 
as a template.

